            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> Caesaris Commodi Antonini</del> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> Pii Sarmatici Germanici <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan></del> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>tus</ex></expan> Sabineius Maximus IIvir <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>muros amphitheatri opere tectorio <lb n="6"/>renovavit item aditus et portas <lb n="7"/>novas de suo fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Material: Kraiger-Marmor. Dekorativ eingestreute hederae besonders in den Zeilen 1 und 7.</p>
            </div>
